Our instance supports a large number of sub-companies, each with their own unique blueprint requirements (different markets/services etc). While you can restrict a blueprint to space, spaces are automatically generated from our finance system based on new jobs etc (and administering this would be an absolute pain). Being able to restrict blueprints to members of group XX (in our case, XX being the group for that companies employees) would be a great way of resolving this IMO.

