If you put a full-sized image on a page (no thumbnail) and load the page, it loads the image once. But when you click on it to view it in the previewer (E.g. to annotate it or zoom in), it re-loads the same image again rather than reading it from the cache. 

We should update the previewer to load the already loaded image on the page

